                  \r\n                    <h1>\r\n                        <img src=\"/images/logo_print_bw.png\" alt=\"Geocaching.com\" />\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"HalfRight AlignRight\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <h1>\r\n                        GCD11E\r\n                    </h1>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Clear\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div id=\"Content\">\r\n                \r\n                <h2>\r\n                    <img src=\"../images/WptTypes/11.gif\" alt=\"Webcam Cache\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Charles Bridge Webcam-Prague\r\n                </h2>\r\n                <div class=\"HalfLeft\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"Meta\">\r\n                        Placed by: \r\n                        SamDeG\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"HalfRight AlignRight\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"Meta\">\r\n                        <span>Placed Date: 07.02.2003</span>\r\n                        \r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Clear\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"HalfLeft\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"LatLong Meta\">\r\n                        N 50\u00b0 05.259 E 014\u00b0 24.636\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"HalfRight AlignRight\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"UTM Meta\">\r\n                        UTM: 33U E 457836 N 5548542\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Clear\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"Third\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"Meta DiffTerr\">\r\n                        <strong>Difficulty:</strong>                        \r\n                        <img src=\"/images/stars/stars1.gif\" alt=\"1 out of 5\" /><br />\r\n                        <strong>Terrain:</strong>\r\n                        <img src=\"/images/stars/stars1.gif\" alt=\"1 out of 5\" />\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Third AlignCenter\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"Meta\">\r\n                        <strong>Size:</strong>\r\n                        <img src=\"../images/icons/container/not_chosen.gif\" alt=\"Size: Not chosen\" />&nbsp;<small>(Not chosen)</small>\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Third AlignRight\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p class=\"Meta\">\r\n                        <strong>\r\n                            Favorites: </strong>\r\n                        9\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"Clear\">\r\n                </div>\r\n                <p class=\"Meta\">\r\n                    <strong>Log Counts:</strong>\r\n                    <img src=\"../images/logtypes/2.png\" alt=\"Found it\" />&nbsp;3&nbsp;Found it&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/logtypes/4.png\" alt=\"Write note\" />&nbsp;18&nbsp;Write note&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/logtypes/5.png\" alt=\"Archive\" />&nbsp;1&nbsp;Archive&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/logtypes/11.png\" alt=\"Webcam Photo Taken\" />&nbsp;394&nbsp;Webcam Photo Taken&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/logtypes/22.png\" alt=\"Temporarily Disable Listing\" />&nbsp;1&nbsp;Temporarily Disable Listing&nbsp;<img src=\"../images/logtypes/68.png\" alt=\"Post Reviewer Note\" />&nbsp;1&nbsp;Post Reviewer Note&nbsp;\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"TermsWidget no-print\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <p>\r\n                        <img src=\"/images/attributes/alert-on.gif\" alt=\"Alert!\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" />\r\n                        <span><strong>Please note</strong> Use of geocaching.com services is subject to the terms and conditions <a href=\"http://www.geocaching.com/about/disclaimer.aspx\" title=\"Read our disclaimer\">in our disclaimer</a>.</span>\r\n                    </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"Clear\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <div class=\"sortables\">\r\n                    <div class=\"item\">\r\n                        <div class=\"item-header\">\r\n                            <h2>Cache Note</h2>                          \r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"item-content\">\r\n                            \r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"item\">\r\n                        <div class=\"item-header\">\r\n                            <h2>Short Description</h2>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"item-content\">\r\n                            I am very pleased to present the Czech Republic's first webcam Cache!  Since the Webcam isn't very detailed, I've made this a combo webcam/virtual cache.  The Questions you must answer are: What Languages are on the statues on the bridge? (Hint: there are more than one)\r\nWhat is the Lavka? (Hint: take a good look at the water, but not the river.)\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"item\">\r\n                        <div class=\"item-header\">\r\n                            <h2>Long Description</h2>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"item-content\">\r\n                            Times Square Webcam Virtual Cache<br /><br /><br />SHOW US YOUR SMILE! <br /><br />This cache requires a team effort!<br /><br /><br />What you will need: <br /><br />A GPS <br />A friend at his/her computer with an internet connection. <br />A mobile phone or set time when you will be at the cache site. <br />How to find and claim this webcam virtual cache: <br /><br />Go to the coordinates of this cache.<br /><br />The coordinates get you in the area of the cache. They are not exact coordinates telling you where to stand. You, with the help of your friend, need to \"hunt\" for the cache. <br />Call your friend and have them go to this image, (<a href=\"http://www.hejda.cz/camery/praha1.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">visit link</a>) <br />Smile for the camera and wait for an update! (this webcam updates every few minutes) <br />When your friend sees a good webcam picture, have them right click on the webcam picture and save the image. Then send you the picture so that... <br />When you make your Found it! log entry you can include the picture in the log. <br />Found it! logs without proper pictures will be deleted. Don't log it until you have your picture ready for upload.<br /><br />Disclamers: <br /><br />We do not own or control this webcam. <br />We do not get any warning when this camera is down for mainenance and/or repair. If the webcam is not working, for any reason, a photo taken of you at the cache site is acceptiable. Enshure, that you are seen in the picture and it is obvious that you are at the cache site. <br />This webcam may be reposistion at any time. For the best picture possable you should use a moble phone so your friend can position you for the best possible picture. <br />Original webcam virtual cache idea